data.title: The Reluctant Debutante
data.meta_description: Vintage color British front-of-house card featuring Kay Kendall, Angela Lansbury and Rex Harrison in the 1958 film.An American girl Sandra Dee comes to London to visit her father Rex Harrison and his new wife Kay Kendall , who is determined to make the girl a debutante. 8 x 10 inches. data.text:
Rex Harrison, Kay Kendall, Sandra Dee, Angela Lansbury (starring)

Vincente Minnelli (director)

William Douglas-Home (play, screenwriter)

Vintage color British front-of-house card featuring Kay Kendall, Angela Lansbury and Rex Harrison in the 1958 film.

An American girl (Sandra Dee) comes to London to visit her father (Rex Harrison) and his new wife (Kay Kendall), who is determined to make the girl a debutante.

8 x 10 inches. Very Good, some creasing and small pinholes.

[Book #146569]
